comments: Nick was a great teacher, though the content of the class was not all that interesting. He did try to make it more exciting by adding a few "fun" assignments. He was really great at giving feedback and my writing style and content really improved because of it. He\'s a bit of a chatter-box and can get off topic, but overall he explains content well.

There\'s tons of writing in this class and homework assigned every day. Attendance is taken every day, so you need to be there or ur grade will be dropped. The teacher is a nice guy and is always available to help you. The class is hard, but if you want to get better at writing, that\'s just what you have to do.
I hate this class, but its a requirement. Nick is a nice guy but the class is so boring and the assignments are really hard and take forever to finish.
Super nice guy, made it so we only had 4 papers to write all semester!
